name: Self Portrait During Avatar Mirroring and {Self} Fragmentation [Cryptoborg #16]
description: The Cryptoborg avatar operates as a digital identity puzzle-box with the possibility for creating multiple mirror psyches that seamless switch from one IDᵠ to another. As an example of ego infolded latent space the avatar program contains psycho maze-markings, ID-keys, {self}codes and riddles for internal ego condensation based on data observed in networks trained on over four billion individuals.  In order for the IDᵠ to be consistent, the avatar program fragments – and then reassembles itself –  while in operation.
